{"type":"text","timestamp":1778601509474,"sessionID":"ses_1e3175243ffehaPV1OwgL5rM1c","part":{"id":"prt_e1ce94152001FFmRYrB7VAd5Xy","messageID":"msg_e1ce8f9ba001T8svo3UCqNRZSp","sessionID":"ses_1e3175243ffehaPV1OwgL5rM1c","type":"text","text":"The prior structural wins point toward retiming hot control/datapath cones, not adding IPC machinery. I’m going to write a structural hypothesis that removes the remaining live WB-stage result mux from the EX forwarding path by carrying registered MEM/WB forwarding data/tag, preserving the current load-use and stall behavior.","time":{"start":1778601509202,"end":1778601509474},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_093821cfa7cea7ac016a034e2516908194810ee6bb9613c45f","phase":"commentary"}}}}
