{"type":"text","timestamp":1778604484150,"sessionID":"ses_1e2e9e654ffeMK1yIcOvcSmUMJ","part":{"id":"prt_e1d16a513001Oo3eONf6PqcOsr","messageID":"msg_e1d168cad0012HzqLReWpwC2Gg","sessionID":"ses_1e2e9e654ffeMK1yIcOvcSmUMJ","type":"text","text":"The structural history shows one clear Fmax win from retiming forwarding selects, while fetch buffering, MEM bypass, WB-data registering, and sideband pruning all regressed. I’ll target the remaining hot structural path by changing stage placement rather than adding prediction or new bypass muxing.","time":{"start":1778604483859,"end":1778604484149},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08d58ada5cb42f57016a0359c3bcf0819088952d3a131184ae","phase":"commentary"}}}}
