{"type":"text","timestamp":1778610721317,"sessionID":"ses_1e28cc88affe66v0go10HofS0Q","part":{"id":"prt_e1d75cbc6001DGCfAwKRcldEJQ","messageID":"msg_e1d73af50002UMybVUgWhZuCO7","sessionID":"ses_1e28cc88affe66v0go10HofS0Q","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor data points all point to the same failure mode: fetch-path control predictors lose more Fmax than they recover in branch bubbles. I’m going to write a predictor hypothesis that avoids the IF next-PC path entirely by predicting exact trivial `MUL` result classes and bypassing the registered multiplier only for those cases.","time":{"start":1778610719686,"end":1778610721316},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a2d46313b0abee7016a03721f89b48190baab16f31955cd8c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
