{"type":"text","timestamp":1778612690464,"sessionID":"ses_1e26ef0b2ffe6cCz4OUX98cXnz","part":{"id":"prt_e1d93d539001i8KiCPXTBIZBoW","messageID":"msg_e1d91887d001WzduQAfp8dnq1R","sessionID":"ses_1e26ef0b2ffe6cCz4OUX98cXnz","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts mostly lost through same-cycle IF next-PC cost and prediction metadata. I’m writing a narrower predictor hypothesis that uses a resolved-redirect target-instruction replay cache, so normal fall-through fetch keeps the existing `pc+4` path and only redirect cycles attempt a cached target inject.","time":{"start":1778612688185,"end":1778612690463},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_053d9b96e69b5e20016a0379d007e0819894744ed79a6ebf9d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
