into unreset LUTRAM read banks can cost more write fanout and LUT/read-mux routing than it saves in resettable flops, so the reset-cleared flop regfile was not the binding CoreMark timing/area path.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/LESSONS.md","time":{"start":1778616489855,"end":1778616489909}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_009dfc4ff09270de016a0388a9b9d48198a9effb2dcbce613d"}},"id":"prt_e1dcdd76a001rU02h6hN9J92Nc","sessionID":"ses_1e2326672ffeu6SPYP8feizLrS","messageID":"msg_e1dcd9a00001MBg2pCLMIEYYmM"}}
