{"type":"text","timestamp":1778606567132,"sessionID":"ses_1e2ca626fffeExf3EPXJIrSnI3","part":{"id":"prt_e1d366e34001V95kWM2XdPRGTQ","messageID":"msg_e1d3615620010dOybnFhLPW2Wd","sessionID":"ses_1e2ca626fffeExf3EPXJIrSnI3","type":"text","text":"The history shows every predictor that touched the same-cycle IF next-PC cone regressed. I’m going to propose the narrowest remaining predictor: an ID-stage fall-through annul for unconditional direct JAL, using the existing redirect interface and no branch/BTB lookup in IF.","time":{"start":1778606566964,"end":1778606567131},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f6798fb8de32cc3016a0361e6ddc881968c46924d4aee23a1","phase":"commentary"}}}}
